Max height in data at \{ ans_rule(10) \} years.

$PAR
b) Which statement, included in your plot command, would correctly set the axis labels on this graph in R?
$BR
\{ $radio1->buttons() \}

$PAR
c) What statement best captures the relationship between TreeAge and TreeHeight?
$BR
\{ $radio2->buttons() \}


END_TEXT

